{"id": "1446806809074602066", "channel_id": "1446806809074602066", "type": 0, "author_id": "984914637126516767", "author_name": "serialexperimentsmid", "author_bot": false, "content": "The existing official art is nice but I find it kind of hard to reference when trying to draw Fan Art, especially since you can't really deviate from the standard outfits if the character is unique like Castor or Faros.  Given how diverse the bodies are in this game it would be nice to be able to create outfits for characters accurately. For example it would be amazing if Ryker's fur pattern was specified so that people could draw him in casual or summer clothing accurately.", "timestamp": "2025-12-06T10:13:43.654000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 5}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1446806809074602066", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Will official character design reference sheets of Awakeners and Characters be created?", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361169005435420785"]}
